com.mcc.ul
Class AoCalConfig

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.AoCalConfig

public class AoCalConfig
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods to get or set calibration settings of an analog output subsystem on a DAQ device. To create an instance of this class, call the getCalConfig() method of the AoConfig class.
